<h2>How to take screenshot on Asus Zenfone 3 using recent apps button</h2>
<p>
  <img
    src="Taking-screenshot-on-Zenfone-3-using-recent-apps-button.png"
    alt="Taking screenshot on Zenfone 3 using recent apps button"
    width="500"
    height="500"
  />
</p>
<p> </p>
<ul>
  <li>Tap on "Application"</li>
  <li>Tap "Settings"</li>
  <li>Choose "ASUS customized" from options.</li>
  <li>Then Choose "Key settings"</li>
  <li>Now Choose "Tap and hold to get screenshot"</li>
  <li>Navigate to the screen you want to capture.</li>
  <li>Press &amp; hold recent apps button</li>
  <li>The screenshot will be taken!</li>
</ul>
